## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-103">根據預設，類別的 Help 關鍵字由提供<xref:System.Type.FullName%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-103">By default, the Help keyword for a class is given by the <xref:System.Type.FullName%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-104">成員的完整名稱之類型的宣告屬性，再加上本身的屬性名稱是給定的 Help 關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-104">For members, the Help keyword is given by the full name of the type that declared the property, plus the property name itself.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-105">例如，請考慮<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType>控制項。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-105">For example, consider the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-106">類別關鍵字會是"System.Windows.Forms.Button"，但<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>property 關鍵字是 「 System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text"，因為<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性宣告上<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control?displayProperty=nameWithType>類別，而非<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType>類別本身;<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType>類別繼承的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-106">The class keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Button", but the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text", because the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is declared on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control?displayProperty=nameWithType> class, rather than the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> class itself; the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> class inherits the property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-107">相反地，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性宣告上<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType>類別中，因此其關鍵字是 「 System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-107">By contrast, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is declared on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> class, so its keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult".</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-108">當 [說明] 系統取得關鍵字時，它會先查看<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-108">When the Help system gets the keywords, it will first look at <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-109">在類別層級，它會傳回所指定的字串<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-109">At the class level, it will return the string specified by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-110">這不會使用有問題，仍會反映實際完整名稱的宣告型別，以及成員名稱之類型的成員。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-110">This will not be used for members of the type in question, which will still reflect the declaring type's actual full name, plus the member name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-111">這個屬性支援具有相關聯的一般文件不同說明 Id 但的強型別的類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-111">This attribute supports strongly typed classes that have associated common documentation but distinct Help IDs.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-112">下列程式碼範例示範如何將屬性放在成員本身來覆寫這個說明系統行為。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-112">The following code example shows how to override this Help system behavior by placing the attribute on the member itself.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-113">這些是針對下列類別，稱為關鍵字`DemoComponent`:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-113">These are the keywords for the following class, called `DemoComponent`:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-114">Class 關鍵字:"`System.ComponentModel.Component`」 (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent`)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-114">Class keyword: "`System.ComponentModel.Component`" (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent`)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-115">Property1 關鍵字:"`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property1`"（預設值）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-115">Property1 keyword: "`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property1`" (default)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-116">為 property2 的內容關鍵字:"`SomeNamespace.SomeOtherClass.Property2`」 (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property2`)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-116">Property2 keyword: "`SomeNamespace.SomeOtherClass.Property2`" (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property2`)</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
[HelpKeywordAttribute(typeof(Component))]  
public class DemoComponent : Component  
{  
    public string Property1  
    {  
        get  
        {  
            return "";  
        }  
    }  
  
    [HelpKeywordAttribute("SomeNamespace.SomeOtherClass.Property2")]  
    public string Property2  
    {  
        get  
        {  
            return "";  
        }  
    }  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-117">下列程式碼範例示範如何使用<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>類別來指定內容關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-117">The following code example demonstrates using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute> class to specify a context keyword.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5cbee-118">如需這個程式碼範例的完整說明，請參閱[How to： 在 Windows Form 控制項中套用的屬性](~/docs/framework/winforms/controls/how-to-apply-attributes-in-windows-forms-controls.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5cbee-118">For a complete explanation of this code example, see [How to: Apply Attributes in Windows Forms Controls](~/docs/framework/winforms/controls/how-to-apply-attributes-in-windows-forms-controls.md).</span></span>  
  
